---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import WhatsAppButton from '../components/WhatsAppButton.astro';
---

<Layout title="Nadi Astrology History - Ancient Palm Leaf Predictions">
  <Header />
  
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">
          Nadi Astrology History
        </h1>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-6">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            The history and practice of ancient Nadi Astrology began many centuries ago. This mystical science originated from enlightened sages who possessed divine knowledge about the past, present, and future of humanity.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-800">Origins of Nadi Astrology</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Thousands of years ago, great sages and rishis of India wrote the destinies of people on palm leaves using their yogic powers. These sages, including Agastya, Kaushika, Vashista, and Bogar, could see into the future and documented the life paths of individuals who would seek guidance.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-800">The Sacred Palm Leaves</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            The palm leaf manuscripts are written in ancient Tamil script and contain detailed information about individuals' lives. Each leaf is identified by the unique thumb impression of the seeker, making it a highly personalized form of astrology.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-800">Vaitheeswaran Koil Connection</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Vaitheeswaran Koil temple in Tamil Nadu became the primary center for Nadi Astrology. The temple dedicated to Lord Shiva as the God of healing attracts seekers from around the world. The spiritual energy of this sacred place enhances the accuracy and power of Nadi readings.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-primary/10 border-l-4 border-primary p-6 rounded my-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-800">Key Historical Facts:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li>✓ Dating back thousands of years to Vedic times</li>
              <li>✓ Written by enlightened sages with divine vision</li>
              <li>✓ Preserved on palm leaves in ancient Tamil script</li>
              <li>✓ Centered around Vaitheeswaran Koil temple</li>
              <li>✓ Passed down through generations of Nadi astrologers</li>
              <li>✓ Continues to guide seekers worldwide today</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-secondary transition-colors">
            Experience This Ancient Wisdom
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
  <WhatsAppButton />
</Layout>
